The paper discusses the use of deep learning in business analytics and operations research, which involves machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) techniques. The paper also discusses the use of real data, which falls under the category of data science (cs.DS). The paper also discusses the managerial implications of using deep learning, which falls under the category of operations management (cs.OM) and computational engineering (cs.CE).
